headline: INCY Q4 Deep Dive: Revenue Growth Outpaces Profit as Pipeline Advances, Margins Narrow
summary: Biopharmaceutical company Incyte Corporation (NASDAQ:INCY) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 27.8% year on year to $1.51 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.80 per share was 6.1% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
